article.description: — Charlie Brown had 19 points in Saint Joseph's 77-59 victory over Sacred Heart on Monday night.
article.headline: Brown scores 19, Saint Joseph tops Sacred Heart 77-59
article.linkText: Brown scores 19, Saint Joseph tops Sacred Heart 77-59
article.story:
PHILADELPHIA -- — Charlie Brown had 19 points in Saint Joseph's 77-59 victory over Sacred Heart on Monday night.

Brown added 11 rebounds for the Hawks (5-6). Kacper Klaczek had 13 points and Lynn Greer III scored 11.

Joey Reilly led the Pioneers (5-8) with 15 points, four assists and two steals. Raheem Solomon added 13 points and Bryce Johnson scored 12.

Saint Joseph's led Sacred Heart 35-18 at the half.
